# Build context for the relay image is the MONOREPO ROOT (see Dockerfile).
# Docker 23+ reads `<dockerfile>.dockerignore` first, then `<context>/.dockerignore`.
# This file is named to match: rename to `Dockerfile.dockerignore` is unnecessary
# because Docker also resolves `<dockerfile-dir>/.dockerignore` for `-f` builds.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
data
**/prisma/data
**/*.db
**/*.db-journal
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm
.git
.gitignore
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.log
.DS_Store
docs
README.md
LICENSE
skill
packages/cli
packages/core
**/.dockerignore
**/Dockerfile
